LIBRAWDIST
==========

librawdist - A Rust library for managing packages in the Rawssg ecosystem.
Create, fetch, verify, install, and remove `.rawdist` archives with
built‑in integrity checks and atomic manifest handling.

Version  : 0.3.2
License  : GPL-3.0
Website  : https://github.com/mroczect/librawdist
Rust     : Edition 2024


